---
// Componente CTA (Call to Action)
---

<section class="bg-azul-une py-16 md:py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Contenido centrado -->
    <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <h2
        class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight"
      >
        Empieza a transformar tu futuro hoy
      </h2>

      <div class="text-white text-base md:text-lg">
        <p>Da el primer paso hacia la carrera que mereces.</p>
        <p>Nuevos grupos cada 5 semanas.</p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center mt-2 md:mt-4"
      >
        <a
          href="/contacto/solicitarinformacion"
          class="bg-rojo-une text-white font-semibold text-base md:text-lg px-10 md:px-12 py-3.5 md:py-4 rounded-full inline-block transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0"
        >
          ¡Empezar ahora!
        </a>

        {/* Botón A/B Test - Inscríbete */}
        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScyrURKYXtsBliCbWEgFt0FJU0j2wYuOrqc6QooqnWQ4AVG8A/viewform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="bg-white text-azul-une font-semibold text-base md:text-lg px-10 md:px-12 py-3.5 md:py-4 rounded-full inline-block transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0"
        >
          Inscríbete
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
